		<title>The Unmappable Made Present &#8211; 4pm on April 4th, 2012</title>
		<link>http://evoke.ics.uci.edu/unmappable-made-present/</link>
		<comments>http://evoke.ics.uci.edu/unmappable-made-present/#comments</comments>
