		<title>Values in Design Workshop &#8211; August 19-26, 2012</title>
		<link>http://evoke.ics.uci.edu/values-in-design-workshop-2012/</link>
		<comments>http://evoke.ics.uci.edu/values-in-design-workshop-2012/#comments</comments>
